description: Concejo AB engages in the development and sale of products, services, and systems for safety, navigation, and automation applications. The company is headquartered in Nacka, Stockholm and currently employs 200 full-time employees.  The Company’s primary activity is to develop businesses by taking ownership in other entities in order to support and coordinate their actions. Main investments of Concejo AB (publ) include Companies engaged in such operations as supply of firefighting systems for primarily offshore platforms, development of optical gas detectors, fire-fighting foam, production of bio-oil and biogas and providing of cyber security.
naicsSubsector: Securities, Commodity Contracts, and Other Financial Investments and Related Activities
